.vscode/**
.vscode-test/**
src/**
.gitignore
.yarnrc
vsc-extension-quickstart.md
**/tsconfig.json
**/.eslintrc.json
**/*.map
**/*.ts
# tree-sitter-wasms incluye ~40 gramáticas; solo usamos Python. Excluir el resto
# mantiene el .vsix pequeño (cada .wasm pesa cientos de KB).
node_modules/tree-sitter-wasms/out/*.wasm
!node_modules/tree-sitter-wasms/out/tree-sitter-python.wasm
